import React from 'react'
import {  Router, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
// import pages
import Home from './pages/Home'
import About from './pages/About' 
// import components
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Navbar />
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path='/'>
          <Home />
        </Route>
        <Route path='/about'>
          <About />
        </Route>
          
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
